* https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buffon%27s_needle_problem
* https://www.math.leidenuniv.nl/~hfinkeln/seminarium/stelling_van_Buffon.pdf
* https://www.isa-afp.org/entries/Buffons_Needle.html

-/

